Grandpa, we'll go check the blood pressure.

27
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,420
Young people

28
00:01:48,420 --> 00:01:49,720
are not very particular.

29
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,600
Measuring with bare hands?

30
00:01:58,144 --> 00:01:59,200
Good job.

31
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,240
You don't praise me for my quick reaction

32
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:01,600
but criticize me?

33
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,560
My brother and she have left?

34
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,880
They went to his room
to measure blood pressure.

35
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,240
Okay, the blood pressure measurement
is almost done.

36
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,080
- It's time to go out.
- Give me a number.

37
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:21,480
80, 120, all normal.

38
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,320
I'm going to see the dog.

39
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,680
Why seeing a dog?

40
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:29,160
Let me introduce Dr. Tian to you.

41
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,320
No introduction needed, Grandpa, I'm shy.

42
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,960
What are you shy about?

43
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,720
You always mess around.

44
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,720
Okay, let's go.

45
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,960
Grandpa, what's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

46
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,600
My heart feels uncomfortable.

47
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,000
Mr. Han, get me the medicine.

48
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,960
I… I forgot to bring it.

49
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,880
I forgot, it's with me.

50
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,320
Then I'll pour you a glass of water.

51
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,760
- I'll do it.
- Okay.

52
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,880
Grandpa, here's your hot water.

53
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:30,520
Grandpa, you also have a bad heart?

54
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,640
Dr. Tian,

55
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,900
this has been an old problem
of mine for decades.

56
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:40,240
Old problem?

57
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,920
When did it begin? Why didn't I know it?

58
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,840
Shen Mi's father

59
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,840
also had heart problems.

60
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:52,060
He has had a bad heart since he was little.

61
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:54,040
I'm really worried

62
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:56,400
about his physical condition.

63
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:03,940
Dr. Tian, I have an unfair request,

64
00:04:03,940 --> 00:04:07,040
but I hope you can understand.

65
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,520
Grandpa, please go ahead.

66
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,840
I hope

67
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,440
you and Shen Mi

68
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,079
can live together.

69
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,840
What happened to Carlo?
Should we go check on it?

70
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,120
Well, it's okay.

71
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,860
Carlo…

72
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:30,360
It's okay, it might be hungry.

73
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,800
You continue to listen to Grandpa's story.
Don't interrupt him.

74
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,880
Dr. Tian,

75
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,000
the heart problem

76
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,960
might lead to a heart attack.

77
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,000
Besides,

78
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,600
there are precedents.

79
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:48,040
Moreover, it's not convenient for you

80
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,200
to shuttle back and forth every night.

81
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,440
So I think,

82
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,640
why not just live here?

83
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,640
Grandpa,

84
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:57,360
actually I don't bother.

85
00:04:57,360 --> 00:05:00,960
Moreover, living here is also not convenient.

86
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,048
Dr. Tian,

87
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,940
are you married?

88
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:04,960
Or

89
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,760
do you have a boyfriend?

90
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,560
That's me.

91
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,592
She has.

92
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:16,560
None of that.

93
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,600
Well then there's no problem.

94
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:21,240
Sir, wouldn't it be inappropriate?

95
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,000
Dr. Tian is still a young lady.

96
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,120
Living with Shen Mi,

97
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,480
I'm afraid it won't be appropriate.

98
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,360
That would definitely not be good.

99
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,640
Physicians have a benevolent heart.

100
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,920
They heal the sick and save lives.

101
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:37,240
Where is there a gender divide in that?

102
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,040
Don't overcomplicate it

103
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,460
in your minds.

104
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:44,140
This is very normal.

105
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:45,360
Yes.

106
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,160
Dr. Tian,

107
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,360
I beg you,

108
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:55,840
can you save my eldest grandson?

109
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,240
Save me, please.

110
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,840
There's also a younger grandson.

111
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:01,840
If anything really happened to Shen Mi,

112
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,000
I…

113
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:11,080
Grandpa, don't worry, don't get upset.

114
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,160
I…

115
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,760
I…

116
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:18,320
I promise you, is that okay?

117
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,440
Okay.

118
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,880
Then

119
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,400
it's settled.

120
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:28,280
You two must not deceive.

121
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,640
I might

122
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:34,640
come to check unannounced at any time.

123
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,888
Mr. Han,

124
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:43,960
let's go.

125
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,800
We won't disturb the young ones.

126
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,080
Uncle, Grandpa, let me see you out.

127
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:50,100
No need, we can walk on our own.

128
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:52,140
You two chat first, okay?

129
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:53,560
- Take care, see you.
- Goodbye, Grandpa.

130
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,760
Come on, take it slow.

131
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:09,080
Sir, we shouldn't meddle
with this love affair as old men.

132
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,120
It's not good.

133
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,200
Did I?

134
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:14,120
You are not suffering from heart disease.

135
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,760
That time at dinner,

136
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:18,640
you let Mengnan cooperate
with Gu Mingze at work.

137
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,520
You think I don't know what you're thinking of?

138
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,600
I can't hide anything from you.

139
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,160
Didn't you say it?

140
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,080
For young people's affairs,

141
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,120
let them solve them by themselves.

142
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,960
We should stop interfering.

143
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,640
The young people nowadays

144
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:41,344
care about face, think a lot, and do less.

145
00:07:42,144 --> 00:07:45,640
Can't we as elders help them out?

146
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,040
As for the road ahead,

147
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:53,240
they have to walk by themselves.

148
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,760
I don't care anymore.

149
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,976
Come on, please.

150
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:19,640
So this heart disease
is hereditary in your family.

151
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,976
Yes.

152
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:29,200
Oh yes, Grandpa just asked

153
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,760
me to live in your house.

154
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:34,020
I have to go back
and discuss it with my parents.

155
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:37,240
You must discuss it with your parents.

156
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,799
You must have their permission.

157
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,760
No need to discuss,
they definitely won't agree.

158
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:43,080
If they agree, I will

159
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,160
eat the door.

160
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,120
I'm leaving first.

161
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,320
See you in the hospital tomorrow.

162
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,168
Shen Mi,

163
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,680
how did you become like this?

164
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,688
Shen Mi,

165
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,440
