166
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,680
You used these dastardly, shameless
and despicable means.

167
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,960
Even in collusion with Grandpa
to deceive Tian Tian.

168
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,360
Grandpa doesn't have a heart disease.

169
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,080
Believe it or not, I'll report you tomorrow.

170
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,680
If I say it's not true, do you believe me?

171
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,712
I don't believe.

172
00:09:27,712 --> 00:09:29,160
Then do as you please, call her now

173
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,176
and explain everything to her.

174
00:09:30,176 --> 00:09:31,264
I will do it.

175
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,640
You think I dare not?

176
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,960
But you better think it through.

177
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,360
If Tian Tian asks you

178
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:41,560
what is the real relationship
between you and Grandpa,

179
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,360
how would you answer?

180
00:09:51,008 --> 00:09:53,824
<i>[Tianlin Animal Hospital]</i>

181
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,940
Your sister will live with Shen Mi.

182
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:02,120
No.

183
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,160
My sister will live with Shen Mi?

184
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,560
Shen Mi told me herself

185
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:10,560
with the most provocative expression.

186
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,840
He told me in person.

187
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,040
Let me tell you, from today on,

188
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:16,120
Tian Tian is my girlfriend.

189
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,720
Wherever Tian Tian goes, I'll go.

190
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,160
You better stay away from her in the future.

191
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,480
We absolutely cannot let such people
succeed in their schemes.

192
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,560
Exactly.

193
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,920
Don't worry, I have a plan.

194
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,120
The dog.

195
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,600
Oh no.

196
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,632
It's ruined.

197
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,640
Oh my god! God,

198
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:37,360
you have been so good to me.

199
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,920
Whatever I want comes true.

200
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,240
Thank you so much.

201
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,400
Mrs. Tian, can you stop blabbering?

202
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,440
It's been such a long time.

203
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,120
I'm really worried to death.

204
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,840
I've been begging to god.

205
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,160
You guys live together.

206
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:51,960
What have you got to worry about?

207
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:55,060
Can your mind be a little bit purer?

208
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,240
Live together?

209
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,560
What are you thinking about?

210
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,720
At that time, you didn't know
how urgent the situation was.

211
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,400
I agreed out of necessity.

212
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,680
Tian Tian.

213
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:05,920
Tian Tian,

214
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:09,280
your courageous actions deserve commendation.

215
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,280
Don't trash talk me here.

216
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,200
Quickly, help me think.

217
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,940
How should I explain to my parents?

218
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,080
If they ask,

219
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,320
should I just tell them directly

220
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,840
that I'm living with Shen Mi?

221
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:24,760
It seems like you can't tell the whole truth
to my sister-in-law.

222
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,200
Just tell them

223
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,880
you are going to night school
with Wen Jing to study further.

224
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,040
Every day,

225
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,520
it's too late, and you're too tired.

226
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,020
So you stay in the hospital.

227
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:37,160
They won't come to the hospital to find you.

228
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:39,936
Will this work?

229
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,360
Beg me.

230
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,880
I beg you.

231
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,560
Then I beg God.

232
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,168
God.

233
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,560
Not bad.

234
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,720
It's good, right?

235
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,720
Pretty good.

236
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,280
I'm back!

237
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,240
- So late.
- It smells so good.

238
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,800
What delicious food did you make today?

239
00:12:07,232 --> 00:12:08,384
Good. Good.

240
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,240
Speed it up a bit.

241
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,544
Dad,

242
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,600
what is this?

243
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,560
This is a special rehabilitation machine.

244
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,520
Faster.

245
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,520
Tian Tian, you're back.

246
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,720
- Okay.
- Everyone is here.

247
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,160
Who's cooking then?

248
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:28,128
Me.

249
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,640
Of course, it's me.

250
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,640
Mr. Shen, you've worked hard.

251
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,480
- Rest for a while.
- No need, Auntie.

252
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,080
I will serve everyone some rice

253
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,520
and we can start eating, Auntie.

254
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:39,920
You should go wash your hands, Tian Tian.

255
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,960
Go wash your hands quickly.
What are you standing there for?

256
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,640
- Let's eat.
- Let's eat.

257
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,840
Well,

258
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,280
it's Mr. Shen's first time
coming home for dinner

259
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:57,180
and he's cooking for us.

260
00:12:57,180 --> 00:12:59,800
I feel really bad.

261
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:02,800
It's okay.

262
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:05,280
Did Tian Tian not tell you
that I have a chef certificate?

263
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,680
If you two enjoy the meal,

264
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:08,768
another day…

265
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,080
Another day…

266
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,100
Let's eat first.

267
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:13,120
Let's eat.

268
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,456
Let's eat.

269
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,960
Uncle, Yuxian told me

270
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,640
that this braised pork was your favorite.

271
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,600
It used to be my favorite.

